WEBVTT

00:10.400 --> 00:12.099
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF"...</i>

00:12.101 --> 00:13.232
PASTOR GREENLEAF,

00:13.234 --> 00:15.298
WINSTON PRICE.
WHAT BRINGS YOU DOWN HERE?

00:15.300 --> 00:16.232
CORALIE HUNTER.

00:16.234 --> 00:18.099
THAT POND YOU'RE
ABOUT TO STEP INTO,

00:18.101 --> 00:20.465
IT MIGHT BE A LOT
DEEPER THAN YOU THINK.

00:20.467 --> 00:22.831
-TICKETS TO SEE HAMILTON?
-YES.

00:22.833 --> 00:24.031
ZORA'S ON PUNISHMENT.

00:24.033 --> 00:25.565
IT'S HER 18th BIRTHDAY.

00:25.567 --> 00:27.365
ACTIONS HAVE
CONSEQUENCES.

00:27.367 --> 00:29.199
YOUR MOTHER
IS BEING TOO STRICT.

00:33.900 --> 00:35.032
YOU FOUND MORE CASH.

00:35.034 --> 00:37.232
I TRUST YOU
AND YOUR EXPERTISE.

00:37.234 --> 00:40.232
YOU EMPTIED
OUR SHARED ACCOUNT.

00:40.234 --> 00:44.098
I WANT YOU OUT OF
THIS HOUSE TONIGHT.

00:44.100 --> 00:46.132
I'VE ALREADY MADE
ARRANGEMENTS WITH PERCY.

00:46.134 --> 00:47.799
I GOT THIS MEMORIAL
SERVICE HERE TONIGHT

00:47.801 --> 00:49.932
AND THE SINGER JUST CALLED
AND SAID SHE HAS THE FLU.

00:49.934 --> 00:52.365
I'M NOT SURE I CAN BE
OF COMFORT RIGHT NOW.

00:52.367 --> 00:54.598
Just one or two songs?

00:54.600 --> 00:55.899
I'M HERE
TO BAIL YOU OUT.

00:57.367 --> 00:59.165
WE SHOULD BOTH GO
OVER THERE TOMORROW

00:59.167 --> 01:00.432
AND BRING ZORA HOME.

01:01.434 --> 01:02.432
THANK YOU.

01:02.434 --> 01:04.065
I'M 18 NOW, I'M LEAVING.

01:04.067 --> 01:06.732
AND WHEN PRAY TELL
IS THIS GRAND ESCAPE

01:06.734 --> 01:08.532
OF YOURS TAKING PLACE?

01:08.534 --> 01:10.332
IN ABOUT 10 MINUTES.

01:16.134 --> 01:18.265
ZORA?

01:18.267 --> 01:21.398
ZORA?

01:21.400 --> 01:23.132
ZORA...

01:23.134 --> 01:26.532
YOU GET YOUR TAIL RIGHT BACK
TO THAT HOUSE THIS INSTANT.

01:26.534 --> 01:29.198
MUILLARD. MUILLARD,
OPEN THE GATE, PLEASE?

01:29.200 --> 01:31.598
DON'T YOU OPEN
THAT GATE, MUILLARD.

01:31.600 --> 01:33.198
I AM 18, I'M FREE.

01:33.200 --> 01:34.798
OPEN THE GATE,
PLEASE, THANK YOU.

01:34.800 --> 01:36.798
DON'T YOU DARE TALK
TO ME ABOUT FREEDOM.

01:36.800 --> 01:39.865
YOU'RE JUST A PRISONER OF
YOUR OWN PRIDE AND CONFUSION.

01:39.867 --> 01:41.565
OKAY, SO I'M GONNA
CLIMB OVER THE GATE

01:41.567 --> 01:43.798
AND ESCAPE LIKE THE
PRISONER THAT I AM.

01:43.800 --> 01:45.998
LISTEN TO ME.

01:46.000 --> 01:48.598
YOUR COUSIN NEEDS YOU
RIGHT NOW.

01:48.600 --> 01:49.932
DOES THAT MATTER
TO YOU AT ALL?

01:49.934 --> 01:51.332
NEEDS ME?

01:51.334 --> 01:53.265
I TRIED TO TELL HER GOODBYE
AND SHE DIDN'T EVEN CARE.

01:53.267 --> 01:54.398
CAN YOU PLEASE
OPEN THE GATE?

01:54.400 --> 01:56.165
DO NOT OPEN THAT GATE.

02:01.667 --> 02:03.132
OPEN THE GATE, MUILLARD.

02:06.534 --> 02:08.532
DON'T YOU DARE, NO, NO.

02:08.534 --> 02:10.532
LISTEN, IF YOU WANT
TO BE MISS BIG STUFF,

02:10.534 --> 02:12.132
THEN WHY DON'T
YOU JUST STAY HERE

02:12.134 --> 02:14.331
AND DO IT OUT
FAIR AND SQUARE?

02:14.333 --> 02:15.365
WHAT'S GOING ON?

02:16.633 --> 02:17.899
WELL, YOUR DAUGHTER HAS
GOTTEN IT IN HER HEAD

02:17.901 --> 02:19.265
THAT SHE WANTS TO LEAVE.

02:20.767 --> 02:22.198
SO WHAT ARE THE TWO
OF YOU DOING HERE?

02:22.200 --> 02:23.799
WELL, WE'RE HERE
TO TAKE HER HOME.

02:23.801 --> 02:24.865
OH, WELL, THANK YOU SO MUCH

02:24.867 --> 02:26.265
FOR INCLUDING ME
IN THE PROCESS.

02:26.267 --> 02:28.165
MA, WE JUST DECIDED
THIS LAST NIGHT.

02:28.167 --> 02:29.332
MAE, WE HAVE A RIGHT

02:29.334 --> 02:31.598
TO RETRIEVE OUR
DAUGHTER IF WE WANT TO.

02:31.600 --> 02:34.265
Z, HEY,
HOLD ON, YOU TWO.

02:34.267 --> 02:36.065
Z, GET BACK HERE.

02:36.067 --> 02:37.399
LEAVE ME ALONE, GET AWAY!

02:37.401 --> 02:39.999
HONEY, WE'RE HERE
TO TAKE YOU HOME.

02:40.001 --> 02:41.798
-I'M NOT GOING HOME WITH YOU.
-JUST GET IN THE CAR.

02:41.800 --> 02:43.531
WE'LL TALK ABOUT IT
WHEN WE GET TO THE HOUSE.

02:43.533 --> 02:44.865
GET IN THE CAR.

02:44.867 --> 02:46.532
ZORA,
GET IN THE CAR NOW!

02:46.534 --> 02:49.532
JACOB, SHE NEEDS TO
STAY HERE WITH ME.

02:49.534 --> 02:51.665
I NEED TO BE ON MY OWN.

02:51.667 --> 02:53.932
DO YOU HAVE A PLAN?

02:53.934 --> 02:55.599
I MEAN, WHERE ARE
YOU GOING, REALLY?

02:55.601 --> 02:58.799
[ HORN HONKS ]

02:58.801 --> 03:00.598
Isaiah: ZORA, HURRY UP,
GET IN THE CAR!

03:00.600 --> 03:02.932
OH, THIS JOKER,
HERE WE GO.

03:02.934 --> 03:04.332
POP THE TRUNK.

03:04.334 --> 03:05.532
WHAT ARE ALL THESE
PEOPLE DOING HERE?

03:05.534 --> 03:07.398
-JUST POP THE TRUNK.
-ZORA!

03:07.400 --> 03:09.798
Jacob: THAT'S WHAT
WE GONNA DO NOW?

03:09.800 --> 03:10.799
GET OFF OF MY PROPERTY.

03:10.801 --> 03:12.598
DID YOU HEAR ME? GET OFF
OF MY PROPERTY RIGHT NOW.

03:12.600 --> 03:14.632
YO, YO, WE LIVE,
WE LIVE RIGHT NOW.

03:14.634 --> 03:15.965
YOU KNOW WHAT, LITTLE BOY?

03:15.967 --> 03:17.032
YOU NEED TO GET IN
THIS CAR RIGHT NOW

03:17.034 --> 03:18.665
AND YOU NEED TO
DRIVE FAR, FAR AWAY.

03:18.667 --> 03:21.365
OH, YEAH, WHAT YOU GONNA
DO IF I DON'T, FAT ASS,

03:21.367 --> 03:22.365
HIT ME, HUH?

03:22.367 --> 03:23.965
COME ON, YOU BAD,
HIT ME, COME ON!

03:23.967 --> 03:25.632
NO, NO, NO, NO,
MOVE, COME ON,

03:25.634 --> 03:26.898
BRING THE CAMERA CLOSER.

03:26.900 --> 03:28.565
ALL RIGHT, EVERYBODY,
ALL YOU FANS

03:28.567 --> 03:31.398
OF THIS LITTLE PUNK RIGHT
HERE, ISAIAH HITS GIRLS.

03:31.400 --> 03:33.465
THAT'S RIGHT,
HE HITS GIRLS,

03:33.467 --> 03:35.065
AND NOW I'M ABOUT TO
HIT HIM REAL HARD.

03:35.067 --> 03:36.665
OKAY, HIT ME THEN,
HIT ME, DO IT!

03:36.667 --> 03:38.099
I DID IT ONCE,
I'LL DO IT AGAIN.

03:38.101 --> 03:39.099
LISTEN, LISTEN, LISTEN.

03:39.101 --> 03:40.565
YOU'RE GONNA LET
HER GO WITH HIM?

03:40.567 --> 03:43.932
NO, NO, BUT HIS PARENTS
MIGHT PRESS CHARGES THIS TIME

03:43.934 --> 03:44.932
OR HE MIGHT.

03:44.934 --> 03:46.332
LET HIM,
I COULD GIVE A DAMN.

03:46.334 --> 03:48.399
PLEASE, PLEASE JUST
LET ME DO THIS.

03:48.401 --> 03:49.532
'CAUSE WHATEVER
WE DID LAST TIME,

03:49.534 --> 03:51.265
OBVIOUSLY DIDN'T
WORK, JUST LET ME.

03:51.267 --> 03:53.331
FINE, BABY, FINE.
FINE.

03:53.333 --> 03:55.198
[ HORN HONKS ]

03:55.200 --> 03:56.332
WHAT'S GOING ON?

03:56.334 --> 03:58.065
COME ON,
LET'S GO, BABY.

03:58.067 --> 04:00.431
IS THAT THAT ISAIAH BOY?

04:00.433 --> 04:03.598
LORD, HELP ME, OH, I'M GONNA
WHIP YOUR LITTLE WEASEL BUTT.

04:03.600 --> 04:04.798
NO, JUST GIVE US
A SECOND

04:04.800 --> 04:06.398
TO GET THIS ALL
CLEARED UP, PLEASE.

04:06.400 --> 04:08.665
NO.

04:08.667 --> 04:10.499
HEY, WATCH HOW YOU
SLAMMING MY DOOR, OLD LADY.

04:12.134 --> 04:13.532
THIS BOY BEAT YOU,

04:13.534 --> 04:14.865
TREATS YOU LIKE NOTHING.

04:14.867 --> 04:16.065
WHY DO YOU WANT
TO BE WITH HIM?

04:16.067 --> 04:17.198
YOU DON'T UNDERSTAND.

04:17.200 --> 04:18.198
CAN I TALK TO MY
DAUGHTER FOR A SECOND?

04:18.200 --> 04:20.865
OH, PLEASE, YES,
BY ALL MEANS.

04:20.867 --> 04:22.798
YOU HAVE ALL THE
ANSWERS, SOLVE IT.

04:22.800 --> 04:25.132
MAE, PLEASE JUST SHUT YOUR
MOUTH FOR ONE BLESSED SECOND.

04:25.134 --> 04:26.665
MY DAUGHTER'S ABOUT TO
THROW HER WHOLE LIFE AWAY.

04:26.667 --> 04:28.132
IT'S NOT ABOUT YOU
FOR ONCE.

04:28.134 --> 04:29.265
NO, IT'S ABOUT YOU.

04:29.267 --> 04:32.065
YOU ARE NOT GOING
TO TAKE EVERYTHING

04:32.067 --> 04:33.532
THAT I'VE WORKED
SO HARD FOR YOU FOR

04:33.534 --> 04:35.332
AND DESTROY IT
LIKE THIS, ZORA.

04:35.334 --> 04:36.698
YOU DON'T EVEN
WANT ME AROUND.

04:36.700 --> 04:37.899
Z, BABY.

04:37.901 --> 04:39.565
HEY, LITTLE BOY,

04:39.567 --> 04:40.765
YOU PUT ONE HAND
ON MY DAUGHTER,

04:40.767 --> 04:42.598
ONE HAND, YOU HEAR ME?

04:42.600 --> 04:44.598
-HERE TAKE MY PHONE.
-WHAT, SO YOU CAN BUG ME?

04:44.600 --> 04:46.732
-LATER.
-NO, AT LEAST, PLEASE.

04:46.734 --> 04:49.665
JUST IN CASE YOU WANT
TO REACH OUT, OKAY.

04:49.667 --> 04:51.532
I WON'T CALL YOU.

04:51.534 --> 04:53.065
WHAT, YOU JUST WANT
TO BUG ME OUT, THOUGH.

04:53.067 --> 04:54.132
PLEASE JUST TAKE IT.

04:54.134 --> 04:55.565
HERE, PLEASE.

04:59.501 --> 05:01.298
BE CAREFUL.

05:01.300 --> 05:02.498
PLEASE BE CAREFUL.

05:02.500 --> 05:08.665
♪♪

05:08.667 --> 05:14.932
♪♪

05:14.934 --> 05:17.332
OH, MY GOD!

05:17.334 --> 05:18.732
[ TIRES SQUEALING ]

05:18.734 --> 05:28.532
♪♪

05:28.534 --> 05:29.932
♪♪

05:29.934 --> 05:32.298
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

