05:50.000 --> 05:51.132
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

05:51.134 --> 05:52.532
♪ AMEN ♪

05:52.534 --> 05:55.465
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

05:55.467 --> 05:57.965
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

06:01.200 --> 06:02.432
♪ WELL ♪

06:05.800 --> 06:08.932
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

06:08.934 --> 06:14.465
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

